body:
Add BreadcrumbList JSON-LD schema to every HTML file under v3/ that does not already have it.

Format for each page:
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://crashycrash.github.io/offbeat-website/v3/"},
    {"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"[Page Name]","item":"[full URL]"}
  ]
}

Add inside a script type application/ld+json block. Do NOT remove existing schemas. Report which files were updated.
